# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
O(log N), where N is the absolute value of the dividend A
- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
