Suppose Binary Tree is:
		1
	  /    \
	2       3
		  /
		4
Let func. name be DFS (for explaination only).
DFS(1) = DFS(2, 1) + DFS(3, 1)
DFS(2, 1) = 10 + 2 = 12     // Base case
DFS(3, 1) = DFS(4, 10 + 3) + 0 = DFS(4, 13)
DFS(4, 13) = 130 + 4 = 134    // Base Case
=> DFS(1) = 12 + 134 = 146
