# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
We can solve this question using Two Approaches. (Here I have explained all the possible solutions of this problem).

1. Solved using DFS + Binary Search Tree. (Recursive Approach).
2. Solved using Stack + Binary Search Tree. (Iterative Approach).

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
We can easily understand the All the approaches by seeing the code which is easy to understand with comments.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
Time complexity is given in code comment.

- Space complexity:
